com.pump.plaf

Class ModifierColorPaletteUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.ComponentUI
      • com.pump.plaf.ColorPaletteUI
        • com.pump.plaf.FadingColorPaletteUI
          • com.pump.plaf.ModifierColorPaletteUI

  • public class ModifierColorPaletteUI
extends FadingColorPaletteUI
    This is a FadingColorPaletteUI that changes the color set in use based on keyboard modifiers.

    Here are the different possible color sets this UI uses:

    SHEET_DEFAULT_GRID SHEET_MUTED_GRID SHEET_FLESH_GRID SHEET_EARTH_GRID
    SHEET_DEFAULT_CONTINUOUS SHEET_MUTED_CONTINUOUS SHEET_FLESH_CONTINUOUS SHEET_EARTH_CONTINUOUS
